This code creates an NDA for a list of
companies that the user need to sign before seeing any
other data from the company and keeps a log of who have
signed which data and when

how to operate:
download NDA.py, index_nda.html(from templates), nda.html(from templates), log.html(from templates)
install the following packages:
csv
os
flask
datetime
cohere
reportlab.lib.pagesizes
reportlab.pdfgen

run NDA.py
access web from http://127.0.0.1:5000
pick a company to see
sign the NDA

Admin have access to logs
